parameters:
\SE[2]Phew... I wonder if this is enough for today's
Feminine Power Enhancement Time...? \SE[3]I shouldn't overdo
it too much...

\SE[12]If I suddenly become too much of a grown-up lady,
Lunaroa- sama will be surprised... \SE[13]Worst case
scenario, there's a possibility that she won't even
recognize me...

\SE[12]Even a journey of a thousand miles begins with a
single step...! I won't lose, myself...! I'll do my best
today, and tomorrow too...! \SE[14]There's nothing better
than continuous effort...! ...right!

\SE[16]Hello~. \.I'm playing Love-Struck Maiden again today.
\!\SE[0]How's your progress going?

\SE[12]I'm all set...! \!\SE[13]...or at least, that's what
I want to say...

\SE[42]I mean... I can't really feel confident when all I do
is image training... \SE[43]I'm severely lacking in real
combat experience...

\SE[52]Since I've never been in a relationship with anyone,
all I can imagine is a sparkling marriage... \SE[43]Because,
you know, I'm still not yet....

\SE[12]I don't even know if I should be the one embracing or
the one being embraced... \SE[13]I have absolutely no
experience...

\SE[21]She's hesitating there... Well, it must be something
important... \!\SE[0]I don't really understand, though.

\SE[12]No, umm...? Are you saying that seriously...?
\SE[38]Certainly, experience is the most important thing to
grasp the image, but...

\SE[57]We're friends, so... \!\SE[43]No, precisely because
we're friends...? Hmm...?
\SE[2]What's wrong? What are you talking about?

\SE[14]Hey, I can understand what you're saying too...!?
\SE[12]Why all of a sudden, why are you saying such
dangerous words before lunchtime...!!?

\SE[6]Ah... In summary, you see... \SE[20]Tita said that she
lacks experience, so she wants us to do ecchi with her to
gain experience.
\SE[14]W-Why...!!? \SE[12]Both of you, did you like me...!?

\SE[21]No, well... there's really nothing like that. But...
\SE[20]Tita wants to make use of her experience in case of
an emergency, so she's suggesting that we undergo special
training with us.

\SE[2]Can you really perform ecchi properly with your
current lack of experience without getting nervous in case
of an emergency? \SE[3]After all, there are people who might
lose interest if we go that far and then struggle during the
main event...

\SE[14]What's common is being a tuna.... \!\SE[13]You know,
it might be difficult for some people to properly make
moaning sounds during their first time....

\SE[2]Actually, I'm not really good with tuna either....
\SE[1]You know, it's because it's a form of communication
with the body, so if you don't express your feelings, I
won't understand.

\SE[12]You know, it can be really tough when you don't know
what the person you like is thinking, right? \SE[3]So, it's
better to be able to express yourself. Moaning sounds.

\SE[14] Moaning sounds...!! Are they really that
important...!?

\SE[12]This is important.... Just by doing that, we can
ignite each other, you know. \SE[13]There's no chance for a
girl who can't pretend to be innocent and moan.

\SE[12]I see... \SE[13]The opinions of my seniors are indeed
helpful...

\SE[14]\SM[pop]If that's the case... I'll do it! For the
sake of studying, I'll... engage in ecchi!

\SE[21]Ahaha... Looks like we're going to do it.
\!\SE[0]Well then, let's change the location. If we stay
here, we might run into mom....

\SE[16]It's safe here, right? \SE[0]Since we're going to do
it after all... we should enjoy ourselves.

\SE[27]Why are both of you completely naked...!? \SE[59]And
also, it's so cramped...! The population density is so
high!!

\SE[21]No, no... We can't do it without taking off our
clothes, right...? \!\SE[50]Well, as they say, If you want
to eat at a low table, you have to sit down... So, shall we
enjoy it deliciously...?

\SE[21]This is my first time with a first experience and on
top of that, with a girl, so it's getting me fired up....

\SE[12]I want to become stronger. \SE[13]Really... to the
point where I can protect everyone...

\SE[2]Hmm... I have some free time until it's time to go
out. Maybe I should tease and play with Ryan... \SE[48]

Melissa seems to like coffee. She's mature and composed...
that's the impression I get.

It's a familiar fountain pen... Maybe it's a memento from my
grandmother.
There is a cactus. ... Lunaroa also likes... The cactus...?

It's a flower that Ronoa-chan picked. It's arranged so
beautifully, it's terrifying... She might have a talent for
that kind of thing.

This is Ryan's training sword. You can feel the dedication
from the wear and tear...

Rebecca's whip. The well-worn leather fits snugly in the
owner's hand, while the tip of the fall inflicts a pain that
clings to the victim's body.

It's just an ordinary clock. Time cannot be turned back, but
children are moving forward. ...I can't afford to lose
either.

Books on 'swordsmanship' and 'military strategy' are densely
lined up. Ryan's earnestness is clearly evident...
...Oh? Behind the large books, there's a hidden door...?
Nikita has a bra. No... it's big. Too big.
